Lab Overview

This lab will guide us through the steps in creating a WordPress blog on an Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2) instance.

Objectives
By the end of this lab you will be able to do the following:

- Install, configure, and launch a WordPress blog on an Amazon Linux 2023 instance.

Technical knowledge prerequisites

Good understanding of Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2) concepts, familiarity with Amazon Elastic Load Balancer (ELB) and basic knowledge of database and webserver architecture is required for this lab.

